by WouterJ at 2014-01-29T12:38:09Z

@iamdto yes, I see that the highlighting is broken. However, double quotes are just valid Yaml 1.0, so that shouldn't be the problem. Have you tested it without it and did you discover that changing this will fix the highlighting?

