---------------------------------------------------------------------------

by stof at 2014-01-29T12:55:23Z

@WouterJ double quotes are fine, but ``\`` needs to be escaped in double quoted strings (like in double quoted PHP strings). It may explain why the highlighting is broken

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

by WouterJ at 2014-01-29T12:57:08Z

Ah, thank you @stof  I was wrong: :+1:  :)

Thank you for your fix & research @iamdto

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

by stof at 2014-01-29T13:02:12Z

and note that it is even a matter of making the code example valid, because ``\N`` is a special char in Yaml (see https://github.com/symfony/Yaml/blob/master/Unescaper.php#L67 for the complete list)

